msgid ""
"Google TTS For NVDA could not be loaded because the WASM TTS Engine library is incomplete.\n"
"\n"
"Reinstall Google TTS For NVDA with the complete WASM TTS Engine library."
msgstr ""
"无法加载“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”，因为 WASM TTS 引擎库不完整。\n"
"\n"
"请使用完整的 WASM TTS 引擎库重新安装“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”。"

msgid ""
"Google TTS For NVDA could not be loaded because the WASM TTS Engine library is missing.\n"
"\n"
"Reinstall Google TTS For NVDA with the included WASM TTS Engine library."
msgstr ""
"无法加载“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”，因为缺少 WASM TTS 引擎库。\n"
"\n"
"请使用自带的 WASM TTS 引擎库重新安装“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”。"

msgid ""
"Google TTS For NVDA could not be loaded because the WASM TTS Engine version is not supported.\n"
"\n"
"This add-on supports WASM TTS Engine version {supported}, but found: {found}.\n"
"\n"
"Install a Google TTS For NVDA package that includes the supported WASM TTS Engine."
msgstr ""
"无法加载“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”，因为不支持该版本的 WASM TTS 引擎。\n"
"\n"
"此插件支持 WASM TTS 引擎版本 {supported}，但当前为: {found}。\n"
"\n"
"请安装包含受支持 WASM TTS 引擎的“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”安装包。"

msgid ""
"Google TTS For NVDA could not be loaded because the WASM TTS Engine voice catalog could not be read.\n"
"\n"
"Reinstall Google TTS For NVDA with a supported WASM TTS Engine library."
msgstr ""
"无法加载“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”，因为无法读取 WASM TTS 引擎的 voice 目录。\n"
"\n"
"请使用受支持的 WASM TTS 引擎库重新安装“适用于 NVDA 的 Google TTS”。"

