#: manifest.ini:changelog
msgid ""
"Version 0.5:\n"
"- Added built-in add-on update checking, with optional startup checks, localized update information, in-NVDA download, and handoff to NVDA's add-on installer.\n"
"- Improved Chrome, Edge, and Brave runtime fallback, including skipping Edge when WebView2 is missing and another supported runtime is usable.\n"
"- Improved NVDA compatibility, language-change handling, speech reliability, optional pause shortening, Simplified Chinese and Russian localization, and accessible read-only status fields."
msgstr ""
"版本 0.5:\n"
"- 新增内置的插件更新检查功能，支持启动时自动检查（可选）、本地化的更新信息展示、在 NVDA 内直接下载以及移交给 NVDA 插件安装程序进行安装。\n"
"- 优化了对 Chrome、Edge 和 Brave 运行时的回退机制，包括当缺少 WebView2 且有其他受支持的运行时可用时，自动跳过 Edge。\n"
"- 提高了与 NVDA 的兼容性，改善了语言切换处理、语音朗读稳定性，增加了可选的缩短停顿功能，补充了简体中文和俄语的本地化支持，并优化了只读状态框的无障碍访问。"
